this is an ok movie.this is simon,a charming gentleman and dangerous criminal, runs a human smuggling business from cuba to the u.s. when simon is shot while escaping from u.s. seas patrols andres, a young cuban saves him. simon takes andres under his wing but the relationship quickly deteriorates when andres falls for a beautiful teenage prostitute named maria who is also a protegee of simon's. them the young couple decides to leave cuba and sail to new york, simon bows to make anything in his power to stop them.
